Memory (is) from the Self; ... Understanding, from the Self; Meditation, from
the Self; Thought, from the Self; Conception, from the Self; Mind, from the
Self; Speech, from the Self; Name, from the Self; sacred formulae (mantra),
from the Self; sacred works (karma). from the Self; indeed this whole world,
from the Self.
